                <ol>
                  <li>Contact our corporate sales team</li>
                  <li>Discuss your training needs and group size</li>
                  <li>Receive custom pricing and course recommendations</li>
                  <li>Set up corporate account with admin dashboard</li>
                  <li>Enroll employees and track progress</li>
                </ol>
                <p>Corporate accounts include bulk pricing, admin reporting, and custom branding options.</p>
              </div>
            </details>

            <details class="faq-question">
