              <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>Yes! We offer custom course development:</p>
                <ul>
                  <li>Courses tailored to your specific equipment and procedures</li>
                  <li>Integration of your company policies and standards</li>
                  <li>Custom assessments and certification requirements</li>
                  <li>Branded course interface and certificates</li>
                  <li>Dedicated support and content updates</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Contact our team to discuss your custom training needs.</p>
              </div>
            </details>
